<p sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/latam-bra-configure-fiscal-books.md" sourcestartlinenumber="112">On the <strong sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/latam-bra-configure-fiscal-books.md" sourcestartlinenumber="112">Observation codes</strong> page, you can set up observation codes to adjust ICMS or ICMS-ST amounts.</p>
